<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَيَرَى ابْنُ أَبِي لَيْلَى أَنَّهُ لاَ تَجُوزُ الْوَصِيَّةُ بِالْمَنَافِعِ لأَِنَّهَا مَعْدُومَةٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلِلتَّفْصِيل فِي الأَْحْكَامِ الْمُتَعَلِّقَةِ بِالْوَصِيَّةِ بِالْمَنْفَعَةِ <span class="c2">(ر: وَصِيَّةٌ)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَقْفُ الْمَنْفَعَةِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٨ - اخْتَلَفَ الْفُقَهَاءُ فِي جَوَازِ وَقْفِ الْمَنْفَعَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَيَرَى الْجُمْهُورُ مِنَ الْحَنَفِيَّةِ وَالشَّافِعِيَّةِ وَالْحَنَابِلَةِ عَدَمَ جَوَازِ وَقْفِ الْمَنْفَعَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَيَرَى الْمَالِكِيَّةُ جَوَازَ وَقْفِهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَالتَّفْصِيل فِي مُصْطَلَحِ <span class="c2">(وَقْفٌ)</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>الاِخْتِصَاصُ بِالْمَنَافِعِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١٩ -<span class="c5"> قَال عِزُّ الدِّينِ بْنُ عَبْدِ السَّلاَمِ:</span> الاِخْتِصَاصُ بِالْمَنَافِعِ أَنْوَاعٌ:<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">أَحَدُهَا:</span> الاِخْتِصَاصُ بِإِحْيَاءِ الْمَوَاتِ بِالتَّحَجُّرِ وَالإِْقْطَاعِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِي:</span> الاِخْتِصَاصُ بِالسَّبْقِ إِلَى بَعْضِ الْمُبَاحَاتِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">الثَّالِثُ:</span> الاِخْتِصَاصُ بِالسَّبْقِ إِلَى مَقَاعِدِ الأَْسْوَاقِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">الرَّابِعُ:</span> الاِخْتِصَاصُ بِمَقَاعِدِ الْمَسَاجِدِ لِلصَّلاَةِ وَالْعُزْلَةِ وَالاِعْتِكَافِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">الْخَامِسُ:</span> الاِخْتِصَاصُ بِالسَّبْقِ إِلَى الْمَدَارِسِ وَالرُّبُطِ وَالأَْوْقَافِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>